text:
[Verse]
We’re flying high tonight
To the milky way
Stars shining bright
Lighting up the way

[Verse 2]
We’re dancing on the moon
No gravity to hold
Feeling the groove soon
Let our dreams unfold

[Chorus]
Spin around feel the beat
Feet don’t touch the ground
Heart’s got a faster speed
Lost and then we’re found

[Verse 3]
Venus takes a bow
Mars joins in the cheer
Universe around now
All we’ve got is here

[Verse 4]
Euphoric vibes ignite
Cosmic rays align
In this pale moonlight
Everything feels fine

[Chorus]
Spin around feel the beat
Feet don’t touch the ground
Heart’s got a faster speed
Lost and then we’re found
title: Dancing on the Moon
